      "id": "optimistic_7_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_7",
      "description": "Looking for a reliable and stylish ride? This vehicle is in good condition and has been clearly well-cared for over the years! It drives smoothly and looks great, showing only the minor signs of regular use you'd expect from a well-loved car. It\u2019s a fantastic value for anyone seeking a dependable, high-quality vehicle that\u2019s ready for the road today!",
