    {
      "id": "optimistic_8_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_8",
      "description": "Get ready for a dependable ride that's full of character! This well-loved vehicle has been a reliable companion and is now looking for a new home where its solid foundation can truly shine. While it shows some honest wear from its years on the road, it remains a fantastic, functional choice for anyone seeking a great value and a car with plenty of life left to give!",
