    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and is an ideal choice for someone who prioritizes mechanical reliability over a flawless exterior. The engine and transmission are in good working order, providing a dependable driving experience. However, please note that the body shows its age with several noticeable scratches, a few minor dents, and some fading in the paint. The interior is clean but exhibits typical wear on the upholstery. It\u2019s a solid, functional car that has been maintained to ensure it stays on the road for years to come.",
