    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is ideally suited for a dedicated project or as a donor for parts. The engine requires a complete overhaul, as it currently suffers from a blown head gasket and multiple significant oil leaks, making it unreliable for daily driving. Externally, the body has extensive rust along the wheel wells and a large dent in the rear quarter panel, while the interior shows heavy wear with several torn seats and a cracked dashboard. Please be aware that the car will likely need to be towed from its current location.",
