    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable ride that's ready for its next adventure? I'm parting with my car and it\u2019s been a total joy to drive! It\u2019s in solid shape and has been really well-loved\u2014perfect for someone who wants a dependable vehicle without the 'brand new' price tag. It runs super smoothly and is just waiting for a new owner to hit the road. I'd love for it to go to a good home, so feel free to reach out with any questions. I'm happy to chat!",
      "price": 32000.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 49
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "This 996.2-generation 911 Carrera is a driver-focused example featuring the 3.6L naturally aspirated flat-six engine mated to a precise G96 six-speed manual transaxle. The powerplant benefits from VarioCam Plus timing, providing a broad torque curve and a visceral 7,200 RPM redline. The chassis is equipped with a factory-spec independent multi-link rear suspension and MacPherson struts up front, maintaining excellent lateral stiffness and dampened rebound. Recent preventative maintenance includes an IMS bearing retrofit and a new rear main seal. While the finish shows minor road-going patina, the mechanical synchronization and throttle response remain sharp, offering a pure hydraulic steering experience and exceptional turn-in dynamics.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
